This plugin makes it easy to add Seam Reports and its dependencies to your project.

To install, run: 

forge git-plugin git://github.com/forge/plugin-seam-reports.git

To configure Seam Reports to work with Pentaho Reporting Engine: 

seam-reports setup --provider PENTAHO

To configure Seam Reports to work with JasperReports: 

seam-reports setup --provider JASPERREPORTS

To configure Seam Reports to work with BIRT: 

seam-reports setup --provider BIRT

To add only the api: 

seam-reports setup





